{"tid":1742852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［反省］教育界可以做啲咩","createTime":"2019-11-21T03:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T03:55:15.000Z","uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d424b837762ebe669fb879c5c27992e81b98155","tid":1742852,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"我係一位老師，我眼見屋苑大部分好多都係大陸家長、大陸小朋友，雖然都唔係今時今日既事。<br />\n<br />\n啲大陸媽媽點落嚟大家都深知係啲港豬返大陸娶埋啲大陸婆，一手一腳慢慢將香港搞到今時今日咁。 <br />\n<br />\n剛剛我聽住6歲既小朋友話唔鍾意啲示威者亂咁破壞。你覺得大陸家長會灌輸得啲咩教育俾佢地，再加上CCTVB啲新聞日播夜播。<br />\n<br />\n講真做呢行望住香港既教育制度咁樣，望住香港個未來，仲可以做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n停課依幾日，多次呼籲同行人士出嚟做返啲野，保護學生、遊行、罷工。但可惜眼見身邊既同事仲更早啲返工怕遲到。<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09ad748a5d43106bdf445ddca6952f6f2377026","tid":1742852,"uid":290895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"快啲生仔仲好"},{"pid":"9aeea3d3c53ace77ef78a2a68a30b78a00421db4","tid":1742852,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"慢慢教，唔好令我地既下一代同小粉紅一樣，真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e378e2c1de09d865358bef27a3c444beb8a15df5","tid":1742852,"uid":295774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"有得上堂咪講下中國啲豆腐渣工程，強拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9f46f3aa8c4c219617412da091f0bfd4c40857","tid":1742852,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09ad748a5d43106bdf445ddca6952f6f2377026","tid":1742852,"uid":290895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"快啲生仔仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:55:15.000Z","msg":"今時今日咁既香港 點生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到佢地都辛苦"}]}